    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve pampered this car, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays in pristine condition inside and out. There isn't a single scratch or scuff to be found anywhere. I'm really looking to get my seller profile moving, so I'm offering this gem at a fantastic price. Come take it for a spin, you're going to fall in love!",
