    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen is powered by the S54 3.2L high-revving straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for optimal cam timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, delivering power to the rear wheels via a flawless variable M differential lock. The chassis is mechanically superlative; the notorious rear subframe mounting points have been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly reliability. The factory suspension geometry remains true, with zero play in the bushings or ball joints. This is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle with a clean DME report and no deferred maintenance, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
